items.name: Rage Ward

2% chance in Heists for Orbs of Transmutation to drop as Chaos Orbs instead
1% chance in Heists for Items to drop with Shaper Influence
items.descrText: You must find the sculpture The Catch in a Smuggler's Den or Underbelly Blueprint to be able to equip this

items.name: The Gluttonous Tide
explicitMods: 123% increased Physical Damage
20% increased Attack Speed
Lose all Frenzy Charges on reaching Maximum Frenzy Charges to make the next Bow Attack you perform fire that many additional Arrows
+50% Global Critical Strike Multiplier while you have a Frenzy Charge
40% chance to gain a Frenzy Charge for each Enemy you hit with a Critical Strike

if but for a moment... only to disgorge and do it all again...

11% increased Cast Speed during any Flask Effect
explicitMods: +70 to maximum Life

Gain 12 Mana per Cursed Enemy Hit with Attacks

flavourText: "Death can be outrun with these, but beware!
In running from death, you may forget to live."

socketedItems.secDescrText: Adds a buff that deals Physical Damage over time, while increasing Attack Speed and Life Leech. Killing an enemy while this buff is active refreshes the buff duration, and can grant a Frenzy Charge.
explicitMods: Base duration is 7.00 seconds
Grants 5% increased Attack Speed
1.2% of Attack Physical Damage Leeched as Life
You take 4% of your Maximum Life per second as Physical Damage
You take 4% of your Maximum Energy Shield per second as Physical Damage
25% chance to gain a Frenzy Charge on Kill
socketedItems.descrText: Place into an item socket of the right colour to gain this skill. Right click to remove from a socket.
